text: Sometimes the video conferences did not work, but I was happy to take the sessions by phone.
Back to face to face when possible.
Female healthcare are rude and unsupportive. One in particular is unprofessional, and made me want to self-harm.
Ideally a face to face consultation, however at these very difficult times that was impossible.
We have struggled getting through on the mobile in the evening. We often try all the way from 6.30 to 7.30, the landline isn’t always any better.
